Komfyk Development and Distribution License (KDDL)
==================================================

This is the license document for the komfyk Kernel Project.

What is the konfyk Kernel?
The konfyk Kernel Project is a custom operating system kernel developed by the community of github(core kernel by Aaha3). It is designed to be efficient, modular, and compatible with various hardware architectures.

