On what hardware does it run?
The konfyk Kernel is designed to run on standard 32-bit and 64-bit architectures that support a paged memory management unit (PMMU).

How to contribute?
Contributions to the konfyk Kernel are welcome. Please send your contributions as patches to the maintainer email address listed below.

Maintainer: Aaha3.sh@gmail.com
